│ PHIs are stale. In the specific reproducer the loop-invariant value 'start2'  │
│ is passed through a PHI with a single incoming from the original loop latch.  │
│ After vectorization without scalar epilogue, the exit block's sole            │
│ predecessor may become the middle block (or gains an additional predecessor), │
│ and the PHI lacks the required incoming for that predecessor, violating IR    │
