VectorLoop->getHeader(), Plan, State);\n+\n+    // Also repair pre-existing PHI
nodes in the unique exit block that are not\n+    // modeled as live-outs by
VPlan. These may be simple passthrough PHIs of\n+    // loop-invariant values and
were created before vectorization. After adding\n+    // the edge from
